{"tid":1220354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反送中】為何香港人如能撐到最少 6 月 15 日，能真正構成更大壓力？","createTime":"2019-06-14T03:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T04:05:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"157f9cd34b0deab26fb5e81ad322ac76e5a920d1","tid":1220354,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:52:21.000Z","msg":"我不會寫太多廢話，我只寫最重要的，認同請傳播。<br />\n<br />\n2019 年 5 月 10 日前從中國出口到美國的產品在進入美國後，仍然會被額外徵收 10% 的關稅，這些商品原定會在 2019 年 6 月 1 日被加徵 25% 的關稅，但是 USTR 將這稅率調升的時間延長至 6 月 15 日。<br />\n<br />\n而美國決定之日，其實與送中條例通過之日是相當鄰近。<br />\n<br />\n香港人能否撐到 15 號，將會成為美國會被討論的因素，如果能撐到 15 號，就很有可能令貿易戰至少延長一個月。真正的構成更大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n如果你們覺得我錯，可指正，歡迎質疑和罵我，我沒時間也沒空引經據典寫一堆 reference 去證明，相信現在大家也沒心情去深究對錯。<br />\n<br />\n跟我陣營不同或討厭我的朋友，我也希望你們分享，查證我說的是否有錯。<br />\n<br />\n請根據這資訊，想想我們現在最需要的是甚麼。請明白香港人在做的事情，能有甚麼影響。<br />\n<br />\n文: 鄭立<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%A6%82%E8%83%BD%E6%92%90%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91-6-%E6%9C%88-15-%E6%97%A5-%E8%83%BD%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A6%2582%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2592%2590%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B0%2591-6-%25E6%259C%2588-15-%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%25A7%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%258A%259B%2F&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=d38b959e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A6%2582%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2592%2590%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B0%2591-6-%25E6%259C%2588-15-%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%25A7%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%258A%259B%2F&h=b50c10b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%A6%82%E8%83%BD%E6%92%90%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91-6-%E6%9C%88-15-%E6%97%A5-%E8%83%BD%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B/</a>"},{"pid":"1e3f732bd03fd2d2615db7529d26c2ec41e881e4","tid":1220354,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"美國時間"},{"pid":"72ae8f85d762ef5f85a6c394b376f0c3a16b84c5","tid":1220354,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:05:05.000Z","msg":"所以香港時間616大遊行真係終極一戰"}]}